Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.62,0:00:05.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那個孩子說想去看海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.45,0:00:08.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但我卻沒能帶她去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:11.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她有很多想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.89,0:00:14.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但我卻什麼忙都沒能幫上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:18.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}夏天明明才剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:39.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.41,0:00:43.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人  早上了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:50.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:28.51,AIR Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,770)}羽   翼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:40.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}霧島同學能變得精神起來 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.94,0:02:41.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:45.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我看到那根羽毛的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:47.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不知為什麼 也有種不可思議的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:50.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:52.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊? 你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:55.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}早晨起來後你就一直在發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:59.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  做了一個孩童時代的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:02:59.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:01.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:04.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}倒是你  還在繼續做著那個夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:06.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:09.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}昨晚的那個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:11.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}和目前做過的夢截然不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:14.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}天上掛著一輪月亮 皎潔耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:17.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}而我  正在試圖衝向天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:21.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}向著高處邊飛邊感覺到身體陣陣作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:24.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}然後我聽到了聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:25.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.42,0:03:27.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是很多人的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:29.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}他們想把我封印起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:32.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的耳朵中嗡嗡轟鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:34.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就再也飛不高了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:37.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好了  一會見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:38.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:40.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:42.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  小心別…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:42.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:55.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇～姐姐你看  好棒耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:59.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}明明沒用繩子  是如何讓它走起來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎呀  摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:05.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哈哈  又站起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:08.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小孩子就應該是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:12.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}對了  你不去陪著佳乃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:16.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哦… 今天做飼養員的工作所以去了學校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:19.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什麼嘛  我們怎麼會在若無其事的交談
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:22.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好了  咱們得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:23.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:26.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小人偶  再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:30.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嘻嘻  握手握手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:31.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.57,0:04:32.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:39.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這就是所謂的情同手足吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我又白幹了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:51.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴這傢伙真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:01.56,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}遠野
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:04.82,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  是國崎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:06.29,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:09.60,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}想說話就先把東西嚥下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:13.04,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}多謝  我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:15.02,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}粗茶淡飯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:17.17,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴沒來過這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:18.67,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神尾同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:19.80,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:20.66,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:24.52,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}吶吶  明天也給我做煎肉餅好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:25.41,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:26.44,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:28.20,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真是貪吃的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:36.80,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}放～手～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:38.90,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你先放！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:42.60,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小～滿～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:07.43,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}淋浴可以使用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:08.36,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.92,0:06:11.24,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你怎麼會有這裏的鑰匙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:16.54,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的父親曾經是這裏的站長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:20.07,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}雖然現在已經辭職了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.43,0:06:22.92,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}現在在做其他的工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:28.04,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}對了  這個表示剛才的歉意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:29.07,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:33.35,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}然後今天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:34.72,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:38.33,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  是小滿昨天找到的瓶子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:40.79,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這個是  星之沙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:46.11,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}像星星的小寶寶一樣的沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:48.55,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎～ 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:49.07,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:53.87,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇～ 沙沙作響呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.59,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}國崎先生也有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:56.38,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:59.08,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這是給我的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:03.55,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊  這樣就每人都有了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:11.62,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這星之沙是我從父親那裏得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:14.51,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那時我還很小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:17.08,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那豈不是非常的珍貴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:18.57,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:22.59,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  給國崎先生和小滿的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:29.77,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴同學  像是已經回去了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:31.28,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:36.11,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看來是在學校停留到很晚才走的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:37.52,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:42.45,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}對了  國崎先生接下來準備做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.72,0:07:48.17,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}歡迎來到天文部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:52.21,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇～ 已經可以看到星星了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.34,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}其他的成員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:57.14,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒有其他成員的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:07:59.58,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只有我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:00.47,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:03.20,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以我就是部長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:05.03,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這叫少數精銳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.12,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是這樣嗎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:15.08,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那傢伙經常來這嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:19.34,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不  這是第一次帶她來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:26.76,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那個  邀請您來沒有給您添麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.89,0:08:27.57,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.87,0:08:30.06,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:37.03,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我一直想三個人一起進行天體觀測來著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:41.32,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為那孩子像是很喜歡國崎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:43.28,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這不太可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:44.18,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:47.20,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那孩子和我在一起的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:50.85,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}總是說國崎先生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:55.05,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那孩子是喜歡國崎先生的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:56.93,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真是讓人難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:59.24,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我看的出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:03.41,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為那孩子是我的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:04.37,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你的一半？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:09.73,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我和小滿一直就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:12.82,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一起生活過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:18.59,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好可愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:19.36,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啵～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:21.97,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}國崎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:22.69,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:27.08,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一直是在一個人旅行是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:31.25,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有過像這樣感受到溫暖的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:36.09,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}感受到和其他人在一起時的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:39.84,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}感受到為了誰而活著的愉悅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:43.94,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我也  應該是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:46.58,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}雖然已經是很久以前了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:52.07,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那小滿就回去了～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.76,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好  明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:56.08,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那小滿就  衝啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:10:01.29,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不好意思  讓您特意送我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:02.91,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:05.11,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你個子挺高的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:08.79,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}您不喜歡個子高的女孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:11.74,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不  體型好是優點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.56,0:10:12.97,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啵～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:17.58,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}其實我對此也多少有點得意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:19.28,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:20.56,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:26.60,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為個子高的話  就會比別人離天空更近一些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:31.06,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}感謝您送我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:32.18,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用這麼認真
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:35.49,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}請您也路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:36.11,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:37.90,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:40.22,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  那位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:43.67,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}天文部的新成員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:44.34,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:47.65,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  你是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:50.48,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}上次真是太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:52.57,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不是說過麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:55.11,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}前些時候幫忙搬過東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:10:59.54,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不好意思  讓您特意送我女兒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:01.77,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好了  快進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:02.65,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小…滿…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:06.89,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼了  小滿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:09.52,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}飯已經做好了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:12.57,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:15.64,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  遠野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:16.75,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:26.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:37.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴  我進來了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:45.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:47.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}會著涼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:51.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  是往人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:52.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:53.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}現在是晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:57.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}補習很晚才完的話  告訴我一聲多好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:00.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}抱歉  我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:02.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:07.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這是？ 你在做繪畫日記？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:11.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  暑假作業中的自由課題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:13.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:17.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}師傅！ 你為什麼背叛了我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.03,0:12:18.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}開什麼玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:22.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}憑你也敢對此大言不慚！ 真是笑死人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:25.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}閉嘴！ 我不說誰說！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:27.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}把○○○交給我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:30.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那麼想要的話  打倒我來搶吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:32.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可惡！ 看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:36.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}爆炎·GOD FINGER-----!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:38.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:40.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}現在正是最精彩的時候呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:45.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}來打撲克吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:49.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你這傢伙真難纏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:52.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好想和往人一起打撲克啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:55.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:56.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:12:58.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}無論如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:12:59.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:03.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好吧  就陪你玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:06.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:07.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}玩什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:09.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}「抽王八」 還是「POKER」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:12.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}簡單的不需要動腦子的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:15.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就玩「湊對兒」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:24.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:26.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:30.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:31.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:33.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:44.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你在哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:46.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我沒哭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:51.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我能玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:55.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我要加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:57.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}必須加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:14:00.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼了  哪不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:01.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:04.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:09.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:10.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你怎麼了  喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:12.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}振作點！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:16.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:18.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:19.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:21.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你先出去一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:23.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴  冷靜點  觀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:43.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那孩子  從小時起就一直如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:47.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}和誰要成為朋友時就會變得那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:50.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要成為朋友時？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.69,0:14:52.96,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也找診所的大夫看過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.11,0:14:54.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也去過大醫院就診過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:56.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但就是治不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:15:02.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}說是什麼心理上的疾病  長大了自然就會好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:06.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}其實  今天在學校她也發作了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:10.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}工作中接到電話  我就騎著摩托去接她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:12.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}然後把她送回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:13.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:19.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我本希望她與你在一起時會沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:23.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她和我在一起時倒是沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:35.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的要離開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:38.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她和我在一起時會發作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.05,0:15:40.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以我和她保持一段距離看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:42.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:45.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}幫我轉告她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:48.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我依然會繼續接送她去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:51.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}時常也來吃頓飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:05.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}由於我的原因  往人無法住在我家了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:08.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一個人孤零零的  不寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:09.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}生活起居一個人也可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:12.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不知不覺朋友多起來了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:15.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你不也是一樣  有朋友在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:17.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不  我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一直都是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:22.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我一旦要與別人成為朋友時  就會哭起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:25.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以大家都遠離我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:28.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但是晴子在你身邊啊 你不會孤單的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:30.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:33.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}其實不是我的親生母親
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.79,0:16:35.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:39.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}晴子其實是我的叔母
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:43.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}由於我是個奇怪的孩子  所以被硬塞給了別人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:45.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}雖然晴子叔母最初也不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.51,0:16:49.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但最終我還是在這裏生活了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:52.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但是  我不想給晴子叔母添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:55.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以雖然同住一個屋檐下  但我們各自過著生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:58.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以我什麼也不奢求
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:00.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已經是個多餘的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:03.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為了不再給別人多添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:05.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我總是自己一個人玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:08.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}找怪怪的果汁喝啦  自己打撲克啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:12.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:16.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}笑一笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:20.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}ｖ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:23.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:24.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:29.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:33.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}美風沒有來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:34.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}去學校了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:36.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到時候就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:40.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天明明不是去學校的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:53.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小滿… 做錯什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:56.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}借給我試試
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:17:58.96,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}還給我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:17:59.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒事  看著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:04.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要啦  間接接吻好髒的  喂～！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:04.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別要求那麼高了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:13.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:15.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}再來一個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:25.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}肥皂泡真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.26,0:18:29.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}透明的  像天空一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:32.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:33.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:36.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是不是出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.19,0:18:41.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}去美風家看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:43.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}去美風家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:46.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  她不來咱們去找她就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:49.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:52.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不想去她家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:54.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你們不是朋友麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:55.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒有去過她家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:18:58.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那我自己去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:01.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為還得去接觀鈴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:05.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}謝謝你送我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:07.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不好意思  我這就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:10.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不來吃晚飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:12.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有個地方要去  明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:13.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:21.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:22.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}昨天我們見過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:24.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那個天文部的新成員
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:25.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:27.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}稍微有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:28.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}能叫一下你的女兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:30.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}女兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:31.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她出去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:34.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我家並沒有女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:37.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}您是不是找錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:41.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  開什麼玩笑  喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:44.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你不去幹活  在這幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:49.73,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}美風的母親一直得有心病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:53.16,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}每次有機會我都會去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:58.69,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她一直把長女美風看作是未能出生的二女兒小滿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:00.85,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}從很早以前就開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:04.93,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但她的癥狀似乎突然間發生了變化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:08.80,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在她明白過來二女兒小滿根本不在了後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:10.64,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}美風的存在也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:17.04,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在她腦海中  兩個女兒變得從一開始就是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:31.42,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我本來應該有個妹妹的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.95,0:20:35.09,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一個叫小滿的  我心愛的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:38.84,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我是爸爸帶大的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:41.96,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以媽媽好像一直都很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:44.70,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}即將誕生的小滿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:48.20,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}本應該可以填補媽媽的那份寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:52.48,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如果美風的一個願望可以實現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:53.71,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}美風會許什麼願呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:58.67,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯… 想要一個妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.91,0:21:02.57,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽失去了心靈的寄托
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:06.35,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以選擇了在夢中生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:10.60,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我… 便是那夢中的一塊殘片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:12.67,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但是昨天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:16.43,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}聽霧島大夫說媽媽夢到了小滿流產時的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.99,0:21:18.73,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}按照霧島大夫的解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.97,0:21:22.15,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽也因此接受了現實
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:27.59,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今早  媽媽看著我對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.15,0:21:29.30,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}「你是誰」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:33.62,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}已經無法回到從前了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.92,0:21:37.58,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這就是我的夢的結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.71,0:21:41.91,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是我以小滿的存在而活下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:43.63,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}夢的結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:50.53,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的翅膀已經忘記了如何飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:52.85,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為我一直以來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.28,0:21:57.00,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只是重複著拍打翅膀的樣子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.06,0:22:02.79,AIR context 6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}無法飛翔的翅膀  還會有意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.16,0:23:42.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你回來啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.42,0:23:45.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}比起我來  也許你更適合旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:47.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}跟我走吧  遠野
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.37,0:23:52.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}果然  這樣下去是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.70,0:23:56.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想讓你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.55,0:23:57.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.69,0:24:00.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不再是夢  是真真正正的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.39,0:24:07.25,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一切的一切  都是我的罪孽造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.98,0:24:09.99,AIR Title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1430,1080)}{\fad(1000,0)}繁   星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.85,0:01:02.74,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}消失的航跡雲 我們目送遠去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:06.45,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}因眩目而逃開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:16.50,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}因懊悔而放手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.30,0:01:23.84,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}尚未抵達之地仍在遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:30.80,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}只有將願望深藏心中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:39.15,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}孩子們走在夏日的鐵軌上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:45.82,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,640)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}手中是將振翅高飛的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:53.83,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}消失的航跡雲 我們追了又追
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:02:02.88,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}從越過這山丘的那天起 就不曾改變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:09.55,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}總是執著不斷前進著的我們
